Rating: 4
This is a great light, fresh dish for summer. The other reviewers are probably right about the oil. I used the whole cup of vegetable oil and could easily have done with less. If I try making it again I'll use a 1/2 cup of olive oil.

Rating: 3
Maybe I initially overcooked the shrimp, but I think marinating for over 24 hours creates very overcooked shrimp. I think the marinade continues to affect the shrimp - like a cerviche. Other than that, it was great!

